headline.main: Leicester Register Back-To-Back Wins With 3-1 Hull Victory
headline.print_headline: Leicester Register Back-To-Back Wins With 3-1 Hull Victory

lead_paragraph: Leicester City made it two wins from two since the sacking of former manager Claudio Ranieri with a 3-1 Premier League victory over fellow strugglers Hull City on Saturday.
